snort

example snort rule:
alert tcp $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET $HTTP_PORTS (msg:"LOCAL suspicious user-agent (Malwarename)"; flow:established,to_server; content:"GET"; http_method; content:"|0d 0a|User-Agent|3a| Malwarename"; nocase; http_header; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:10000001; rev:1; metadata:affected_product Any, attack_target Client_Endpoint, deployment Perimeter, tag User_Agent, signature_severity Major, created_at 2022_03_21, updated_at 2022_03_21;)
